{"tid":341733,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"救助!Setup唔到個router","createTime":"2017-07-31T04:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T01:24:58.000Z","uid":43734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79185fad0631674f72fcc783618290ea231bde56","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"各位巴哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 麻煩幫幫手<br />\n尋日細嘅買咗個dlink嘅router<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/124646_01dd515cb27aaa01f931a1371f30da99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F124646_01dd515cb27aaa01f931a1371f30da99.jpg&h=e7967bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁好正常地個default ip address都係192.168.1.1㗎啦，但係我打完入去之後唔知點解會去咗一個tplink嘅setup page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整咗成日都整唔到 (有試過彈返入dlink個setup page, 不過30秒到就505 error)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/124659_c9e51540625c79cd22300c2fc825cfe7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F124659_c9e51540625c79cd22300c2fc825cfe7.jpg&h=93edb02a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s 喺澳洲租屋住，唔知係咪入咗人哋unit啲router setup page"},{"pid":"97c4061481f93bb3e36474d29af70519b6f3d296","tid":341733,"uid":37107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"插線搞"},{"pid":"0634b7a75c2fb853d80db91ff48d0447aec64e54","tid":341733,"uid":81703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"你條網線是否人地個router分出來比你?"},{"pid":"680acdd465cbe5f83e81afae29d90f39f6536660","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>插線搞</blockquote><br />\n點插線搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f03d2573b807a4b5d8fd02bc48eb46a09e676a3","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你條網線是否人地個router分出來比你?</blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊會唔會係，但係我之前幫個frd搞佢又冇事(佢用netgear)"},{"pid":"9fdea678ced86a3b4c1d8ca21ea1be4b41d4e87a","tid":341733,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>插線搞</blockquote><br />\n點插線搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n電腦直吉router<br />\n再入192.168.1.1 改ip"},{"pid":"c6098e3d7586ece5fd5e8602a8515a0f6c9fbad6","tid":341733,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"好似係0.1唔係1.1喎"},{"pid":"6b4ac107e6c44fdb82310bb9146a141f65a41129","tid":341733,"uid":24785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"比返個router 人地啦"},{"pid":"033aef2b6f168f2bf95d7d97f62d574d1fc1b14e","tid":341733,"uid":6530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似係0.1唔係1.1喎</blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\ndlink係192.168.0.1"},{"pid":"ea5c813229a0e454a86ebc701dd9a96e005299ed","tid":341733,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"你個wifi入左人地network<br />\n你應該搵返自己d-link個wifi再setup<br />\n<br />\n搞掂左唔該自己捐200$去無國界<br />\n呢樣係專業知識範疇之一"},{"pid":"d583312615d6d0d7db53f9d83e80a485c2ca319e","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>插線搞</blockquote><br />\n點插線搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n電腦直吉router<br />\n再入192.168.1.1 改ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想改ip address, 吉唔入呀我用mac"},{"pid":"a1170a06e996af80e3463fcef4592dd17c821023","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似係0.1唔係1.1喎</blockquote><br />\n我個router default ip寫192.168.1.1"},{"pid":"030cacc3ca4aa3dacffb8f211ae49b681079a042","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比返個router 人地啦</blockquote><br />\n佢俾返我得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d89b481aa1052dc86aad22dbcf2ce91149da89d","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個wifi入左人地network<br />\n你應該搵返自己d-link個wifi再setup<br />\n<br />\n搞掂左唔該自己捐200$去無國界<br />\n呢樣係專業知識範疇之一</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你意思係wifi signal嗰到？我係sure我入dlink喎<br />\n<br />\n雖然搞唔掂不過會去捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx 巴打"},{"pid":"58f3fdd8c2682538e23175c7017c6cf3bf7da7da","tid":341733,"uid":24015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>插線搞</blockquote><br />\n點插線搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n電腦直吉router<br />\n再入192.168.1.1 改ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想改ip address, 吉唔入呀我用mac</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三樣野，人地個router(primary)/你部router(secondary)/PC<br />\n<br />\n總之你要斷開後兩者同primary既連接，pc淨連secondary<br />\n之後重新開機，入ip去setting page，做晒setting改埋ip再接返晒佢地<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93ff4fe7d52b472ae465e4c12a9c629bf5d8247","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"我借我個frd個垃圾router嚟試都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呀！俾我setup啦大佬，邊條撚樣喺apartment到用tplink呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259f8f26941c46221594b681e38f33e072a88911","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>插線搞</blockquote><br />\n點插線搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n電腦直吉router<br />\n再入192.168.1.1 改ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想改ip address, 吉唔入呀我用mac</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三樣野，人地個router(primary)/你部router(secondary)/PC<br />\n<br />\n總之你要斷開後兩者同primary既連接，pc淨連secondary<br />\n之後重新開機，入ip去setting page，做晒setting改埋ip再接返晒佢地<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThx ，咁就仆街啦，我連primary喺邊都唔撚知，無望啦，嘥撚咗20aud呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b40e3f56ab87a9e0cbe24bb4526f19c5234114","tid":341733,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"全屋得呢舊撚嘢同internet有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/31/164202_fc14e7cec85ef2dfa4ea33e4d11dd4cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2F164202_fc14e7cec85ef2dfa4ea33e4d11dd4cb.jpg&h=aa528e84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"785f32d1b1eb8613c3afc1a0257b3472614acd36","tid":341733,"uid":24015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>插線搞</blockquote><br />\n點插線搞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n電腦直吉router<br />\n再入192.168.1.1 改ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想改ip address, 吉唔入呀我用mac</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三樣野，人地個router(primary)/你部router(secondary)/PC<br />\n<br />\n總之你要斷開後兩者同primary既連接，pc淨連secondary<br />\n之後重新開機，入ip去setting page，做晒setting改埋ip再接返晒佢地<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThx ，咁就仆街啦，我連primary喺邊都唔撚知，無望啦，嘥撚咗20aud呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwifi既話我都唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你部電腦無lan者，你可以拎去俾有lan既朋友set架嘛"},{"pid":"856d4c41bfb107846fe5d581879aa86d8db5c9d0","tid":341733,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"應該冇internet都可以setup個router，試吓先斷開router連接internet既lan線，就咁用部電腦連接router個wifi去setup"},{"pid":"fc6101b3955cf9ba0e46a83ad304c159c9e2b6fd","tid":341733,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個wifi入左人地network<br />\n你應該搵返自己d-link個wifi再setup<br />\n<br />\n搞掂左唔該自己捐200$去無國界<br />\n呢樣係專業知識範疇之一</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你意思係wifi signal嗰到？我係sure我入dlink喎<br />\n<br />\n雖然搞唔掂不過會去捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx 巴打</blockquote><br />\nDouble check一次sure係d-link network入面<br />\n因為router-router係兩個地方黎<br />\n<br />\n如果再係咁 <br />\n建議先抆走wan線 得你同你隻router wifi駁住再入<br />\nOr 買usb to rj-45<br />\n<br />\nBtw 你部機之前有無做過關於tp-link setup<br />\n都有極細機會係cache問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一係你部router比人洗左做tp-link既rom?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4602356c90710e9bbbef62a4decded5c830cc1c3","tid":341733,"uid":2209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"不如用手機set啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}